;(First interaction)
::<!--Trigger PerformanceE 502025101: Config/Level/NPCDialogue/P10202/F10202001_G43/Act/Act_502025101.json-->
::'''Guangda:''' Ah, two centuries passed, and then two centuries more... If I don't get my promotion, I'll undergo my hatching rebirth soon...
::{{DIcon|Arrow}} Promotion?
:::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_502025103-->
:::'''Guangda:''' Yeah. In one of our lifetimes, Vidyadhara have to serve as officers or clerks so we get a taste of what it's like to be a public servant, right?
::{{DIcon|Arrow}} That's a real shame.
:::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_502025105-->
:::'''Guangda:''' Sure is. Unfortunately, we're the only ones who think it's a real shame. If only management felt the same way.
::{{DIcon|Arrow}} In your next life, go all out.
:::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_502025107-->
:::'''Guangda:''' Haha, I'm afraid that I'll be a lowly orderly in my next life. I've started to wonder how exactly things ended up during my previous life.
::<!--Custom String Trigger: TalkSentence_502025108-->
::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_502025108-->
::'''Guangda:''' Hey, that's enough for now. Let's not linger on such a morose topic.
::'''Guangda:''' I'm Guangda, a lowly orderly from the Realm-Keeping Commission. If you have any issues to handle, I suggest you visit our Chancery offices...
;(Subsequent interactions)
::<!--Trigger PerformanceE 502025102: Config/Level/NPCDialogue/P10202/F10202001_G43/Act/Act_502025102.json-->
::'''Guangda:''' Please head inside the Chancery office for any official business. I'm just a lowly orderly...
