:{{DIcon|Talk}} Did you notice the Ambrosial Arbor was growing once again?
::<!--Trigger PerformanceE 502025301: Config/Level/NPCDialogue/P10202/F10202001_G52/Act502025301.json-->
::'''Guangda:''' How could I miss it!
::'''Guangda:''' Drop it. The Seat of Divine Foresight put out a mandate demanding that we stand on strict guard duty during this sensitive period of regrowth. We absolutely cannot afford any secondary problems to occur.
::'''Guangda:''' *sigh* Please don't let there be another accident. Please don't let there be another accident... If anything else happens, they'll take my pension away.
::'''Guangda:''' ...Or at least, please don't let there be any accidents in my jurisdiction...
::<!--Ends the current performance-->
::<!--Custom String Trigger: Talk_502025301-->
;(If {{Mission|Obsequies Performed, A Long Road Ahead|showChapter=0}} has been completed and {{Mission|Wood Sprouts Anew, Fate Tilts Askew|showChapter=0}} has been completed, {{cx}}<!--performance 502025301 has been seen-->, and {{Mission|Obsequies Performed, A Long Road Ahead|showChapter=0}} has not been completed)
:{{DIcon|Talk}} Do you know that the Ambrosial Arbor no longer sprouts?
::<!--Trigger PerformanceE 502025104: Config/Level/NPCDialogue/P10202/NPCAct/Act502025104.json-->
