::'''Guangda:''' It is tiring, but it's worth it... After working so hard to protect the peace, we can finally loosen up a bit.
::'''Guangda:''' I can really use a break, and I already have plans in my mind for what I want to do during the vacation... I'll spend a few days going on a trip and enjoying good food... just the thought of it puts me in a good mood.
